        "subject": "LU-2959 mgc: allow mgc_copy_llog to fail early in OST startup",
        "message": "LU-2959 mgc: allow mgc_copy_llog to fail early in OST startup\n\nIf a lock is canceled before mgc_fs_setup has completed, it's possible\nto call mgc_copy_llog with cli->cl_mgc_configs_dir not set, in this\ncase, fail gracefully instead of ASSERTing and dieing.\n\nSigned-off-by: Nathaniel Clark <nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ic6e34549838894913daea832880f3d0160b98d70\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
